Package com.foreach.across.modules.bootstrapui.elements.icons

Class IconSetRegistry

java.lang.Object
com.foreach.across.modules.bootstrapui.elements.icons.IconSetRegistry
public class IconSetRegistry extends Object
Is used to add, remove or get an IconSet from the IconSetRegistry collection. If you are looking for an easy way to render or get an immutable icon, you can use the IconSet.icon(String)
Since:
3.0.0
Author:
Stijn Vanhoof
